<h1>Audit (A-04-11-01003)</h1>

<h2>04-13-2012<br />
Centers for Disease Control and Prevention Did Not Meet Program Expansion Supplement Requirements for Awarding One Affordable Care Act Grant</h2>

<div id="related" style="width: 232px; padding-bottom: 0px;">
<h3>Related Content</h3>
